## Coding Standards
- Components: Use Functional Components with named exports
- Styling: ALWAYS use Tailwind classes via className
- Data Fetching: Use React Query with Supabase
- Error Handling: Use toast notifications
- Types: Strict TypeScript usage. No `any`

